Colom guarantees Portillo's extradition to the United States
Guatemalan President <0xC3><0x81>lvaro Colom announced Tuesday that he would approve the extradition of former governor Alfonso Portillo to hold him accountable in the United States for the $70 million money laundering conspiracy.
